    <span class="section-label">What We Build</span>
    <h2>Commercial Construction Expertise</h2>

    <div class="services-grid" style="grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem;">
      <div class="service-card">
        <h3>Retail Construction</h3>
        <p>From standalone stores to multi-tenant retail centers, we understand the unique demands of retail construction. We coordinate MEP systems, storefront installations, and interior finishes while minimizing disruption to adjacent tenants and maintaining tight schedules for your opening date.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card">
        <h3>Office Buildings</h3>
        <p>Ground-up office construction and commercial renovations designed for modern workplace needs. We specialize in creating functional, attractive office environments with careful attention to technology infrastructure, HVAC systems, and energy efficiency.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card">
        <h3>Industrial & Warehouse</h3>
        <p>Heavy-duty construction for manufacturing, distribution, and warehouse facilities. We handle large clear spans, high bay construction, loading dock coordination, and industrial-grade utilities. Our experience includes concrete tilt-up, structural steel, and specialized industrial systems.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card">
        <h3>Tenant Improvements</h3>
        <p>Transform existing commercial space to meet your specific business needs. Whether it's a medical clinic, professional office, or retail space, we excel at tenant improvement work that maximizes your space while coordinating with building management and adjacent tenants.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card">
        <h3>Commercial Renovations</h3>
        <p>Update and modernize existing commercial buildings. We handle everything from cosmetic refreshes to comprehensive remodels involving structural modifications, systems upgrades, and code compliance improvements—all while working around your operational needs.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card">
        <h3>Ground-Up Construction</h3>
        <p>Complete new construction from foundation to final finishes. We manage site work, utilities, building envelope, interior systems, and all trades to deliver a turnkey facility ready for your operation. Our comprehensive approach ensures seamless coordination at every phase.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Our Approach -->
<section class="section-white">
  <div class="container">
    <div style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;">
