      <h2>The Northway Construction Process</h2>

      <div style="margin-top: 3rem;">
        <div style="margin-bottom: 3rem; padding: 2rem; background: var(--color-light-bg); border-radius: 8px;">
          <h3 style="color: var(--color-accent);">Dedicated Project Management</h3>
          <p>Every project receives a dedicated project manager who serves as your single point of contact. They coordinate all trades, manage the schedule, handle problem-solving, and keep you informed with regular updates. You'll know exactly who to call and what's happening at every stage.</p>
        </div>

        <div style="margin-bottom: 3rem; padding: 2rem; background: var(--color-light-bg); border-radius: 8px;">
          <h3 style="color: var(--color-accent);">Quality Craftsmanship</h3>
          <p>We work with skilled, reliable trade partners we've built relationships with over two decades. Our standards for quality are non-negotiable, and we conduct regular inspections to ensure work meets both code requirements and our own elevated expectations.</p>
        </div>

        <div style="margin-bottom: 3rem; padding: 2rem; background: var(--color-light-bg); border-radius: 8px;">
          <h3 style="color: var(--color-accent);">Transparent Communication</h3>
          <p>No surprises. We provide detailed proposals, clear change order processes, and regular progress updates. When challenges arise—as they do on any construction project—we communicate proactively with solutions, not just problems.</p>
        </div>

        <div style="margin-bottom: 3rem; padding: 2rem; background: var(--color-light-bg); border-radius: 8px;">
          <h3 style="color: var(--color-accent);">Safety First</h3>
          <p>We maintain comprehensive safety programs and ensure all work complies with OSHA requirements and industry best practices. A safe jobsite is a productive jobsite, and we take our responsibility to workers and the community seriously.</p>
        </div>

        <div style="padding: 2rem; background: var(--color-light-bg); border-radius: 8px;">
          <h3 style="color: var(--color-accent);">On-Time, On-Budget Delivery</h3>
